Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:31.35,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I thought it might \Ncome back out if I called to it...}Chị định gọi nó ra để nựng...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:33.56,Main,Senpai,0,0,0,,{That's what you were doing?!}Chị gọi được nó hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:36.30,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It was the cutest thing you ever saw!}Nó dễ thương lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:39.19,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{A tiny brown kitty, about this big...}Bé mèo màu nâu nhỏ xíu cỡ này...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:43.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Really fluffy and soft!}Mềm và mịn lắm luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:46.20,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I already know you are, though.}Chị đang giới thiệu bản thân hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.58,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I was talking about the cat.}Con mèo mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.66,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Right! Of course! The cat!}Vâng vâng! Là con mèo nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.88,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, look at the time!}A, đến giờ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.79,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Let's get moving, Shinozaki-san!}Đi thôi Shinozaki.
