Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:10.97,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Manager.}Quản lý.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:14.91,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I sent the plan for our entry \Ninto the project competition,}Em vừa gửi bản kế hoạch dự án rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.31,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{so please check it, when you get a chance.}Anh kiểm tra lại nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:20.44,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Wait, already? There's still \Na while until the deadline.}Xong rồi á? Vẫn còn hạn mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:24.09,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I know! But since we'll need to \Nincorporate input from the client,}Vâng! Nhưng chúng ta cần \Nđối chiếu với bên khách hàng nữa,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:27.10,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{the sooner we get it checked, \Nthe sooner I can make those adjustments.}nên là nộp sớm để có thời gian chỉnh sửa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:31.63,Main,Katase,0,0,0,,{Makes sense. Well done, Katase-san. \NI appreciate how timely you are.}Hiểu rồi. Cảm ơn nhé Katase. Tôi rất biết ơn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:33.40,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Nice one, Senpai.}Chị tuyệt quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:37.84,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{This is all normal stuff. \NI'm a grown-up, after all!}Bình thường thôi. Chị là người trưởng thành mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:44.97,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I have to say, desk work really does \Na number on the back and shoulders...}Cơ mà việc bàn giấy làm đau vai gáy ghê...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:46.99,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{My whole body feels creaky.}Cơ thể kêu cọt kẹt luôn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:50.43,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's even worse when you're \Non the computer all the time.}Nó còn tệ hơn nếu chị ngồi máy tính cả ngày nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.72,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Definitely...}Phải đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:55.35,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{My shoulders can really seize up on me, too.}Vai chị nặng nề lắm luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:58.87,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I think there might be more to it \Nthan just work, in that regard...}Em nghĩ nguyên do là thứ khác nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:01.86,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's the kind of thing that \Nmakes you want a massage, huh?}Lúc này chỉ muốn được mát xa thôi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, what a great idea! I'd love that!}Ý hay đó! Chị muốn được mát xa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:10.22,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Wait... did I just stumble into a mildly \Nerotic situation involving a massage?}Khoan... mình đang rơi vào tình huống mát xa kích dục?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.15,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Want me to rub them?}Để em bóp cho nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:14.50,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Would you?}Được hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:23.21,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Right there... It feels... so good...!}Phải rồi... ở đó... đúng đúng...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:30.22,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{If you keep that up... I'll...}Nếu cứ tiếp tục... tôi sẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.14,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Something wrong?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:35.38,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{N-No, nothing at all!}K-Không có gì ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:40.65,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I get stiff shoulders, too, so I was thinking \Nabout maybe getting a massage myself.}Vai em cũng bị cứng nên đang định tự bóp đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:46.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sounds like a case where a hardworking \Nkohai needs some senpai encouragement!}Đàn em cố gắng hết sức nên\N cần đàn chị này động viên nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:50.09,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Aw, come on, I couldn't ask you to do that...}À không... chị không cần phải...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:51.76,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Don't you worry about it.}Đừng lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:54.54,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Just don't fall asleep \Nfrom being too comfy, okay?}Đừng thấy sướng quá rồi ngủ là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:03.84,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Squeezey, squeezey, squeezey, squeezey...}Bóp bóp bóp...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:06.52,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai's tiny hands are all over my shoulders!}Bàn tay nhỏ bé của chị ấy \Nđang mơn trớn khắp đôi vai mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:08.99,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm getting squeezed! \NShe's kneading me like dough!}Chị ấy đang mơn trớn kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:11.43,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's like I'm in the world's \Ncomfiest theme park!}Cảm giác như đang vào công viên\N thư giãn tuyệt vời nhất vậy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:18.75,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san, you're so... hard, and big...}Shinozaki... của em... vừa cứng vừa to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:23.44,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I don't know if my hands \Ncan make you feel good.}Tay chị không biết đủ làm em sướng không...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:28.15,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai, uh, I think that's enough!}Chị à, em nghĩ thế đủ rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Did it feel good?}Có tuyệt không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:33.27,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yes! Maybe a little too good.}Vâng! Hơi bị phê quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:36.83,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Er, forget I said anything! Really!}À không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:44.44,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{"And that is my proposal."}Và đó là phương án của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:47.68,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Okay, hopefully that should work.}Rồi, có vẻ ổn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:49.59,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Maybe I should run through it again...}Luyện thêm lần nữa nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:53.40,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{"I'm Shinozaki Takuma \Nwith Dev Group 2's Team A."}Tôi là Shinozaki Takuma nhóm phát triển số 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:56.19,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{"My proposal involves the upcoming anniversary}Về đề xuất liên quan đến ngày kỉ niệm...
