Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.43,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Senpai!}C-Chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:04.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Did I scare you?}Hết hồn hả?
