Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.70,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{so I was practicing during my free time.}em đang luyện tập lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:13.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That takes me back! \NI remember what it was like.}Hoài niệm ghê. Chị cũng từng làm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:18.67,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{And so, by arranging a collaboration \Nbetween popular sweets brands}Và như thế, hãy sắp xếp sự hợp tác giữa \Ncác thương hiệu bánh ngọt nổi tiếng,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:20.99,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{and our company's mascot character, Meowtaro,}và linh vật Nyantaro của công ty ta,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:24.71,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I believe we could cultivate customers \Nin a new demographic.}Tôi tin rằng chúng ta có thể \Nthu hút nhóm khách hàng mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:30.63,sign_10663_99_Meowtaro_Collabo,Powerpoint,0,0,0,,{\pos(193.333,154.667)}{Meowtaro Collabo}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:30.63,Sign_Basic,Powerpoint,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(296,104)\frz180\fs10\b1\c&H696C6B&\bord0\shad0}{Currently popular sweets}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:30.30,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Er, uh, pardon me...!}À, tôi xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.72,0:07:34.01,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I made some goofs \Nwith the materials for my proposal.}Chị nhầm bài phát biểu tư liệu của nhóm chúng ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:38.56,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But as you can see, I'm still here, \Nso relax and give your best shot!}Nhưng em cứ yên tâm, cuối \Ncùng chị vẫn làm việc ở đây nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.98,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What a random bit of encouragement!}Chị tự tin thái quá rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.71,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Senpai.}Cảm ơn chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:48.48,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I just have this tendency to get \Nsuper nervous when it's showtime...}Nhưng em cứ đến lúc quan trọng là lại lo lắng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:52.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{They say writing the kanji for "person" in your \Nhand and pretending to swallow it helps.}Người ta hay nói viết chữ "nhân" lên tay rồi nuốt là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.49,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What do you think?}Em chưa thử nên không biết sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.85,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's probably just a superstition...}Em nghĩ chắc chỉ là mê tín...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:58.27,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Although one theory says the palm \Nhas certain pressure points,}Dù em có đọc qua rằng ở bàn tay có huyệt giảm lo lắng...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:02.56,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{and by tracing the kanji for "person" \Nyou can press them for a relaxation effect—}và bằng cách nhấn tay viết chữ nhân, chị có thể--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.38,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san!}Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.09,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Something to relax you.}Hãy thư giãn đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:10.30,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Specially made by your Senpai, \Nit's the kanji for "person."}Đây là quà của đàn chị đó. Chữ "nhân" cho em.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.09,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I hope you enjoy it!}Hãy nuốt nó đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:16.60,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-So close! Senpai's tiny hand \Nis right in front of me!}G-Gần quá! Bàn tay nhỏ bé của chị ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:20.18,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-It almost seems like a waste to eat it!}P-Phí quá em không ăn đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:24.44,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I can always make more.}Không đủ thì chị sẽ làm thêm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.76,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{So, by all means, eat up!}Thế nên là hãy ăn hết nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:29.11,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She is so wifely, it's killing me!}Chị ấy cứ như người vợ vậy! Chết mất thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:33.11,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Th-Then, in that case, don't mind if I do...}V-Vậy thì em không khách sáo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:43.53,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Uh, er, did my breath tickle?}Em thở hơi mạnh ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:45.88,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, no, it's f-fine!}K-Không sao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{H-How do you feel?}T-Thấy sao rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:50.09,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Better! I think I can do this.}Có vẻ ổn hơn rồi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.76,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Thank you so much, Senpai.}Cảm ơn chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:55.79,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'll be looking forward to another \Ntomorrow, before my presentation.}Ngày mai cũng mong chị giúp đỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:59.06,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Ừm! Chị sẽ đến đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yamagishi-san.}Yamagishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.27,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(518,282)\p1\bord0\shad0\c&HFCFBFD&\blur2}m 0 0 l 180 0 l 180 90 l 0 90
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.27,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(518,282)\fs16\c&H0D0D0D&\bord0\shad0\b1}{Development Group 2\NTeam B, Designer\N}{\fs24}{Yamagishi Aiko\N}{\fs16}{(1st Year of Employment)}Nhóm phát triển số 2\N Thiết kế \N Yamagishi Aiko\N 1 năm vào công ty
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:06.01,Main - Top,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Will you be coming to the \Nend-of-month drinking party?}Cô có tham gia vào buổi tiệc cuối tháng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:07.27,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,Đi chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:09.21,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Cộng một.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:11.21,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{You're organizing, Shinozaki-kun?}Cậu tổ chức à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.78,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I drew the short stick.}Vâng, tôi thua rút thăm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.22,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Hey, Hayakawa, you coming to \Nthe end of month drinking party?}Hayakawa, buổi tiệc cuối tháng này sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.16,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(116,284)\p1\bord0\shad0\c&HF0F8F7&\blur2}m 0 0 l 180 0 l 180 90 l 0 90
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.91,0:09:20.16,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(116,284)\fs16\c&H0D0D0D&\bord0\shad0\b1}{Development Group 2\NTeam A, Designer\N}{\fs24\fscx96}{Hayakawa Chinatsu\N}{\fs16\fscx}{(1st Year of Employment)}Nhóm phát triển số 2\N Thiết kế \N Hayakawa Chinatsu\N 1 năm vào công ty
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:20.78,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I'll pass.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:23.80,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Again? Sociable as ever, I see.}Lại nữa à? Lúc nào cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:26.62,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Quit whining. I attended once, remember?}Im đi, có tham gia 1 lần rồi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:28.76,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah, once. The first time.}Ừ, lần đầu cũng là lần cuối.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.66,Italics - Top,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Stare...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.38,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Once is plenty, isn't it?}Một là đủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.30,Italics - Top,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Staaare...}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.55,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{Are you two going out?}Hai người đang hẹn hò à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:38.68,Main,Shinozaki/Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{What?!}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:42.06,Main,Yamagishi,0,0,0,,{It's just, Shinozaki-kun seems \Nweirdly frank with you, Hayakawa-san.}Chỉ là Shinozaki có vẻ thoải mái khi ở cạnh Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:46.04,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Th-That's not it! Hayakawa...san \Nhere is just a childhood friend!}K-Không phải... Hayakawa là bạn thuở nhỏ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:49.32,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{Yeah, exactly! We just grew up near each other!}Chính xác! Là hai đứa nhà gần nhau!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:54.78,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Dating her? Is that really how it looks?}Hẹn hò à? Mình còn chưa hình dung ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san.}Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:59.40,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Do you and Hayakawa-san get along?}Em với Hayakawa thân nhau nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:00.70,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You, too, Senpai?!}Cả chị nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.54,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's less that and more...}Nói là thân nhau...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.90,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{We were neighbors,}Nhưng do cả hai là hàng xóm,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:09.48,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{and we attended preschool, \Nelementary, and middle school together.}học tiểu học, cấp 1, cấp 2, cấp 3 cùng nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:13.15,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Then we just happened to end up \Nworking at the same company.}Và không biết sao lại vào làm cùng công ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:15.05,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's kinda like we're cursed.}Kiểu như bị dính lấy nhau vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:20.30,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You seemed to be pretty friendly, though.}Nhưng hai đứa có vẻ thân thiết.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.50,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Wait, what? Is she jealous?}Hả? Chị ấy ghen à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:25.85,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{No, come on, Senpai would never...}Không không, làm gì có chuyện...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:30.52,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's really nothing special. \NSure, we chat casually...}Thực sự không có gì đâu. \NĐúng là bọn em có nói chuyện thoải mái...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.27,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm jealous.}Ghen quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:40.48,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-S-Senpai?! She just said she was jealous! \NI did hear that, didn't I?!}C-Chị ấy vừa nói là ghen nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:43.62,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And she does seem to be kind of sulky...}Và có vẻ hơi dỗi nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:47.53,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai's... jealous?}Chị... ghen ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:51.67,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That'd mean she... about me... for real?}Tức là chị ấy thực sự... với mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:55.30,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san.}Shinozaki nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.96,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I...}Chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:05.68,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I... well...}Chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:13.99,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I want to be friends with Hayakawa-san, too.}...muốn làm bạn với Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:20.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I've always thought she seems rather neat,}Lúc trước chị đã thấy em ấy rất tuyệt vời,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:23.20,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{but we've never really had \Na chance to connect outside of work.}nhưng cả hai hiếm khi nói chuyện gì ngoài công việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.77,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{If you wouldn't mind, \Ncould you maybe introduce me...?}Em có thể giới thiệu cho chị không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:26.94,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That's what she meant?!}Hoá ra là thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:29.08,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Hả? Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:33.21,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Just regretting my arrogance, that's all.}Do mình ảo tưởng sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.51,Main,Server,0,0,0,,{Welcome!}Chào mừng quý khách.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:39.12,Main,Server,0,0,0,,{A party of three? I'll show you to your seats.}Ba người ạ? Xin mời.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:50.25,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Y'know, I tend to attract cats for some reason.}Không biết tại sao mà tớ được lũ mèo thích lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:51.50,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I can tell.}Nhìn là hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:55.64,Main,Shiori/Eyecatch Sign,0,0,0,,{\i1}{My Tiny Senpai}{\i0}{!}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:12:02.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{This cardboard box is actually pretty heavy.}Cái hộp này nặng quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:03.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Let me get that for you, Senpai!}Để em giúp cho!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.30,Main,BG Coworker (Female),0,0,0,,{I'm so sorry...}Xin lỗi ạ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:09.66,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{No, no, don't let it bother you.}Không không, đừng lo gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.96,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{These kinds of things happen.}Chuyện này thường hay xảy ra mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:14.17,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Just let me know if you need any more help.}Nếu có gì nhớ báo chị nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.66,Main,BG Coworker (Female),0,0,0,,{Thank you so much.}Vâng ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:17.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san.}Chị Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:19.76,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Did something happen?}Có chuyện gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:22.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{There was a bit of a mix up with some data...}À, dữ liệu bị thiếu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:25.76,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But it should be fine, now.}Nhưng giờ thì ổn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:32.48,Sign_Basic,BG Sign,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(332,36)\fnTimes New Roman\c&H92D5E5&\bord0\b1\4c&H456070&\shad2}{40th Anniversary}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:36.71,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You never seem to get mad at people, Senpai.}Chị ít khi la mắng người khác nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:38.56,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You think so?}Thế hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:39.98,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I mean, just now...}Thì vừa rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.62,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{If someone's already upset \Nabout their mistakes,}Nếu ai đó buồn vì làm sai việc,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:46.99,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm not going to make it worse for them.}chị sẽ không giận họ đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:50.73,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Besides, you can scold someone \Nwithout getting mad at them.}Với cả phải tức giận mới mắng được chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{More importantly, Shinozaki-san!}Cơ mà Shinozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:54.66,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yes?!}Vâng?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:57.56,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You haven't been reporting in enough, lately!}Gần đây em viết báo cáo không đủ đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.96,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I haven't?!}Không đủ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:03.09,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Did I... screw up with work somehow?}Mình... làm sai chỗ nào à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:04.22,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And wait...}Cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:07.22,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Am I getting scolded, right now?}Mình đang bị la sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:10.60,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Uh, well... I...}À thì... em...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:15.35,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{When you work hard, \NI expect you to tell me about it.}Chị muốn em báo cáo mỗi khi cố gắng làm việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:19.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{J-Just when I work hard?}K-Khi cố gắng làm việc á?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Exactly!}Phải!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:25.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I don't want to miss your efforts, \Nespecially when you put your heart into them.}Chị không muốn bỏ lỡ những nỗ lực của em.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.78,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{If this is supposed to be discipline, \Nthen sign me up!}Nếu bị mắng kiểu này thì ngày nào mình cũng muốn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:34.41,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's a senpai's duty...}Là nghĩa vụ của đàn chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:40.63,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{to praise a job well done.}thì khen đàn em là công việc mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:49.34,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Okay, next time I work hard on something...}Vậy lần tới nếu em cố gắng làm việc...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.85,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'll try to make sure and notice, too.}Ừ, chị sẽ cố gắng để ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:55.22,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I appreciate that.}Em cảm ơn ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:02.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Come on, we're back \Nto the office and back to work!}Nào, quay lại văn phòng làm việc thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:05.61,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Right! Wait up, Senpai!}Vâng! Em đến ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:16.17,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's getting late, \Nbut I wanna keep going a bit longer...}Trễ rồi nhưng vẫn còn chút nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:18.87,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Let's finish this up, at least.}Cố hết rồi về.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:28.41,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I bought two by mistake. \NYou're welcome to one.}Chị lỡ tay mua 2 lon. Em uống đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.51,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Thanks so much!}Cảm ơn chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.71,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, I should pay you...}A, để em trả lại tiền...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:35.39,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{No, it's fine, don't worry.}Không sao không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:38.44,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm forcing something off onto my subordinate.}Đây là chị đang ra lệnh cho em đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.63,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Think of it as an abuse of authority!}Cứ xem đó như là lạm quyền đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:44.02,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Best abuse of authority ever!}Muốn được bị lạm quyền!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:47.02,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Are you still not finished for today?}Vẫn chưa xong hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:51.53,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Well, I was just trying to \Nget to a good place to stop...}Vâng, em đang tìm chỗ để kết thúc nó...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:54.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'll help you out!}Để chị giúp cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:58.04,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{But, I couldn't ask you to \Ntrouble yourself, Senpai...}Nhưng em không thể làm phiền chị thêm nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:01.47,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's a senpai's duty to help a kohai in need!}Nhiệm vụ của đàn chị là giúp đỡ đàn em.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:02.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Besides,}Với cả,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.81,0:15:05.82,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{once we're done, I'm going to abuse \Nmy authority and treat you to dinner!}khi nào xong thì chị sẽ ép em đi ăn tối cùng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:08.80,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{They made a sequel to \Nthe best abuse of authority ever!}Muốn được bị làm quyền lần 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:12.17,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Th-then I'd appreciate the help.}V-Vậy nhờ chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.30,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sure!}Ừ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:18.17,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That was faster than I thought!}Nhanh hơn chị nghĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:21.31,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Only because of you. Thanks again, Senpai.}Nhờ có chị đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:23.81,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'll pay for dinner!}Em sẽ trả tiền bữa tối.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.32,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{No, not happening. I'm paying.}Không không, để chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.56,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{No, me!}Không, em!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:28.33,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It'll be me.}Chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:29.05,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Me!}Em!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:29.82,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Me!}Chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:34.73,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's still a bit cold at night.}Chà, có hơi lạnh nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.08,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Come on, let's hurry to the restaurant.}Nhanh đi ăn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.53,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Sh-Shinozaki-san?!}S-Shinozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.58,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Please, just wear it.}Hãy mặc vào đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:44.54,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{B-But...}N-Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.32,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Put your arms through the sleeves, please.}Bỏ tay chị vào ống tay áo đi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.27,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But I... I'll be fine...}Không sao đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.34,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{No, you won't.}Không được.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:53.34,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Y'know, you don't need to have \Nauthority to abuse your power...}Chị không cần phải tỏ ra mạnh mẽ đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:59.60,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I-I'll keep that in mind.}C-Chị sẽ ghi nhớ nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:06.79,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{There should be plenty of places open still.}Giờ này vẫn còn nhiều chỗ mở nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.46,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:12.64,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Um, aren't you cold, Shinozaki-san?}Mà em không lạnh hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:14.49,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Nope. I'm okay.}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:21.02,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{This jacket he lent me is really warm...}Áo khoác em ấy ấm áp quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:25.38,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I guess because he was \Njust wearing it, but still...}Có lẽ là hơi ấm của em...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:29.31,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Something about the size and the warmth...}Kích cỡ và hơi ấm này...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:32.52,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{makes it feel like he's hugging me.}cảm giác như đang được ôm vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:35.89,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Wh-What in the world am I thinking?!}M-Mình nghĩ cái gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:38.42,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{U-um...}À này...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:44.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I-I don't know... \Nif I can continue wearing this...}C-Chị mặc thêm nữa là... không nổi đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:45.94,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What happened?!}Sao thế?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:47.80,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You can have it back!}T-Trả lại em!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:48.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:51.19,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{W-we're almost at the restaurant, so...}C-Chúng ta sắp đến nhà hàng rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{And besides,}Với cả,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:57.45,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{we're close to the office... \NWhat if someone saw?}nhỡ ai thấy thì sao? Đang gần công ty mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:16:59.18,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Good point.}Đúng là vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:03.46,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry. I should have considered that.}Em xin lỗi vì không nhận ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:06.96,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{No, no, I appreciate you letting me wear it!}Không không, cảm ơn vì cho chị mượn áo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:09.64,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Nào, vào thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.46,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm feeling hungry!}Chị đói rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.47,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Right.}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:17.47,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\move(260,96,288,96)\fnTimes New Roman\c&H95C8C5&\3c&HF7FEFE&\shad0\fay.3\frx4\fry22}{Odo Eatery}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:17.47,Main,Server,0,0,0,,{Welcome!}Chào mừng quý khách
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:20.60,Main,Server,0,0,0,,{Party of two? I'll show you to your seats.}Hai người ạ? Để tôi dẫn ra bàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.60,Main,Server,0,0,0,,{The jacket smells like Senpai, \Nand that's a great smell!}Áo có mùi của chị ấy! Quá đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.29,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Something wrong?}Có gì hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:29.61,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I-It's nothing!}Không ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:32.17,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Since it's nice and warm in here,}Trong đây ấm áp quá,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:34.98,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I think I'll take this off.}nên em định cởi ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:39.56,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What should I order...?}Gọi gì giờ ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:43.92,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{There're so many options, \NI don't know where to start.}Có nhiều lựa chọn quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:46.30,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You can take your time to decide.}Chị cứ từ từ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:49.98,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Have you made up your mind, Shinozaki-san?}Em đã chọn xong rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.63,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I think I have, yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:53.76,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Then, I better decide, fast!}Vậy thì chị cũng chọn nhanh luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.80,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You can take your time, really!}Chị cứ từ từ cũng được mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:01.64,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Okay, I've got it!}Hiểu rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:05.14,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(364.667,235.333)\frz24.78\fs18\frx342\fry24\c&H302B2E\bord0\shad0}{Press button for service}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.14,Main,Server,0,0,0,,{I'll be right there!}Có ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:10.57,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'll take the miso-glazed beef tongue \Nand mixed vegetable stew dinner.}Một lưỡi bò hầm miso, phần ăn tối và thêm rau.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:13.63,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{And a fluffy soy milk pudding for dessert.}Tráng miệng bằng pudding sữa đậu nành.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:16.46,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'll have the saikyo-yaki \Ncooked mackerel dinner.}Tôi phần ăn tối saikyoyaki cá thu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.24,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That'll be enough.}Hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What about dessert?}Em không dùng tráng miệng hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.72,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Pudding is really good, y'know!}Pudding ngon lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:26.76,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm a big fan, it's so soft, and sweet, \Nand just plain makes you happy!}Chị thích nó lắm cơ, mềm và ngọt. \NNó khiến em hạnh phúc lắm luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.37,Main - Top,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I'll take one, too, then.}Vậy cho tôi một phần.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:28.92,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Pudding, pudding, more pudding!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.92,Main,Server,0,0,0,,{Understood.}Đã rõ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.81,Main,Server,0,0,0,,{It'll be just a moment.}Xin hãy chờ một chút.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:34.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai, I wanna thank you for your help.}Cảm ơn vì hôm nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And not just for today.}Và không chỉ hôm nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:38.05,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What other day?}Còn hôm khác nữa hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:46.00,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I managed to make it through my project \Nproposal without clamming up, thanks to you.}Nhờ chị mà em đã phát biểu trôi chảy trong buổi gặp gỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.39,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{No, no...}Không không...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:51.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It went well because \Nyou worked hard, Shinozaki-san.}Là do em đã cố gắng hết sức đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:53.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I just helped out a tiny bit!}Chị chỉ giúp có xíu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:58.65,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Besides, I'm obviously going to help \Na kohai who could use it.}Với cả giúp đõ đàn em đan\N gặp khó khăn là bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.41,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Because I'm your senpai!}Vì chị là đàn chị mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:05.50,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{W-Well, I appreciate all that help!}À vâng, từ giờ mong chị giúp đỡ nữa ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:06.79,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Certainly.}Dĩ nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:07.66,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Although...}Cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:11.69,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Don't try and push yourself \Nto work overtime like today, okay?}Đừng cố quá và tăng ca như hôm nay nữa nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:16.17,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Working hard is good, \Nbut overwork is not. Okay?}Cố gắng là tốt nhưng cố quá thì không.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:18.91,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Right!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:20.93,Main,Server,0,0,0,,{Here you are.}Của quý khách đây ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:25.93,Main,Server,0,0,0,,{Saikyo-yaki cooked mackerel, \Nand a miso-glazed beef tongue stew.}Cá thu saikyoyaki và bò hầm miso đây ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.67,Main,Server,0,0,0,,{Please, enjoy.}Xin hãy thưởng thức.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.06,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Come on, let's eat.}Ăn thôi nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:33.05,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{We'll have a nutritious meal,}Một bữa ăn dinh dưỡng,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:36.44,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{and then give it our best at work tomorrow!}và ngày mai lại cố gắng hết mình nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:37.69,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Right!}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:40.57,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Time to eat!}Chúc ngon miệng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Hot!}Nóng!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:43.93,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Are you okay?}Chị ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.37,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah...}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.32,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sensitive to hot food like a cat, too, huh?}Đúng là mèo không thích nóng nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:48.09,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Ý em là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:50.58,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, never mind me!}Không có gì ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:05.19,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Good morning, Senpai.}Chào buổi sáng!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.64,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Good morning, Shinozaki-san.}Chào em, Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:11.35,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Calling out to another cat?}Lại tìm mèo ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:14.23,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Yes, indeed I was!}Còn phải hỏi à.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:17.73,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I heard it meowing a second ago...}Chị nghe tiếng nya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:27.80,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Did you hear that?! It answered me!}Thấy chưa! Nó đáp lại kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:28.83,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Sure.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:35.32,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That was deeper than before, though. \NMaybe there's a second cat?}Cơ mà sao giọng trầm vậy? Con khác à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:44.49,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You! You! I can't believe you made fun of me!}Em! Em đang chọc chị hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:47.47,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry! I didn't think \Nyou'd react like that...}X-Xin lỗi! Em không nghĩ chị lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:51.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{As punishment, for today, \Nyou have to be kitty Shinozaki!}Phạt! Hôm nay em phải làm mèo Shinozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.90,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Kitty Shinozaki...?}Mèo Shinozaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:55.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I expect you to meow in response!}Phải nói nya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:56.56,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{M... Meow.}N-Nya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:58.30,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Y'know, this might be too much...}Cái này có hơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.34,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Excuse me?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:00.82,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's kind of embarrassing—}Nó xấu hổ lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:02.76,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{These are orders from your senpai!}Lệnh từ đàn chị đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:03.52,Main - Top,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Okay...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:06.38,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Do you understand?! You respond with "meow!"}Đã hiểu chưa? Nya đấy.
