Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:09.26,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Oh, good morning, Hayakawa-san.}A, chào em. Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:08.12,Main - Top,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Meow!}Nya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:11.36,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{You look happy. Something good happen?}Trông anh có vẻ vui. Có chuyện gì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:15.56,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Just glad that my team is getting long!}Chỉ là đàn em trong công ty mình thân thiết quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:16.29,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Vậy ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:18.99,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{All right, Meowzaki, we're going to work!}Rồi, Nyazaki! Chúng ta đi làm thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:20.63,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Right, Senpai!}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:23.06,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You're supposed to say "Meow!" Okay?}Nya chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:24.87,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{M-Meow!}N-Nya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:32.22,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Let's give it our best today, Meowzaki!}Hôm nay cũng cố gắng hết sức nhé, Nyazaki!
